data.description: Gated parking. Richardson ISD! Charming ONE STORY Townhome with 2 BR, 2 Baths, spacious Living Room, mirror accent wall in Dining Room. Replaced Kitchen countertops with white quartz, new backsplash, all appliances, and floors in 2017. Breakfast nook in the kitchen for additional dining or space for more cabinets. Wake up in the morning and go directly from the primary bedroom through French Doors to a 22ft x 11ft conditioned SUNROOM. Enjoy this large BONUS Room all year round for hosting dinners, as exercise room, craft room or a combination flex space. Also 50 gal Rheem water heater (2019), Sunroom windows replaced (2017), updated the electrical outlets and electrical panel, and installed French drains in the front and back of home. Quick access to hospitals, airports, and downtown events. HOA amenities include multiple pools, Clubhouse, front yard maintenance, roof coverage, and fence maintenance.
